paternal /pəˈtɜːnəl/

ADJ Paternal is used to describe feelings or actions that are typical of those of a kind father toward his child. 父亲的 

例： ...paternal love for his children. …对他孩子们的父爱。 

2. ADJ A paternal relative is one that is related through a person's father rather than their mother. 父系的; 父亲一方的 [ADJ n] 

例： ...my paternal grandparents. …我的祖父母。

